{"tid":1998711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍：否認昨晚投擲汽油彈案屬自導自演","createTime":"2020-05-02T15:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T16:07:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9896cde5aeee11e2ae9040e4a42f9e00ff79b19b","tid":1998711,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"警方拘15歲少年投擲汽油彈 否認自導自演<br />\n02.05.2020 22:34<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚在太子拘捕一名15歲少年，涉嫌投擲汽油彈，並拘捕一名46歲女子，懷疑少年在她的處所製造汽油彈。警方指，昨晚一輛便裝巡邏車駛經彌敦道近界限街，發現4名男子向路中心擲汽油彈，及拋下插有鐵釘的膠管，警員落車追捕，拘捕15歲少年，在他身上搜獲汽油彈、打火機、和插有鐵釘的膠管，正追捕其餘3名涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n被問到案件會否牽涉警員自編自導自演，警方強調行動不是由情報作部署，只是巡邏時發現有人犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284760&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284760%26csid%3D261_341&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=7fbc5e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284760&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5101b0c85874d148eb4dc69d0d9786da1c03d5e0","tid":1998711,"uid":231583,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.azquotes.com/picture-quotes/quote-never-believe-anything-in-politics-until-it-has-been-officially-denied-otto-von-bismarck-2-75-80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.azquotes.com%2Fpicture-quotes%2Fquote-never-believe-anything-in-politics-until-it-has-been-officially-denied-otto-von-bismarck-2-75-80.jpg&h=ef4997f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a94019ae4aa576b2653c6e046d7ad01e6cdcf47","tid":1998711,"uid":35205,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e120f151c164675aa9a65ee5e22032c44110b2","tid":1998711,"uid":264245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"repl